I follow the argument of both sides, though I think one has more of a leg to stand on.  I can see where each side is coming from, but something Syplh posted bothers me.  <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The total effect of our mistake was to make 3 guilds wait one week each, so what seems reasonable to me is for us to wait 3 weeks for our next KT.<br>
