<br>
--------------<br>
Current Rotation Order:<br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - FK - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - FK - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - FK - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
FK's rotation numbers are 5,13,21,29,...<br>
<br>
--------------<br>
FK jumped ahead of NB on this round which has caused the problems:<br>
SotE - FK - NB - TL - LoM - FK - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - FK - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - FK - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
If nothing is done then FK's rotation numbers are 2,6,14,22,30,...<br>
<br>
I'm pretty sure everyone (including FK) agrees that this isn't acceptable.<br>
<br>
--------------<br>
Karadin's proposed to fix the situation by bumping FK before NB and skipping one rotation:<br>
SotE - FK - NB - TL - LoM - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - FK - NB - TL - LoM - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
If this is done then FK's rotation numbers are 2,17,25,33<br>
<br>
When you look at the original order that means a 1 month punishment because they took a spawn 3 weeks early.  FK is opposed to this because on paper it looks like they are having to skip 2 entire rotations, when really they are only repaying in double what they accidentally took.  NB feels it is fair because it will discourage other guilds from taking spawns eariler than normal. <br>
<br>
--------------<br>
FK's counter-proposal is to leave the rotation as it is, but skip this rounds: <br>
SotE - FK - NB - TL - LoM - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - FK - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - FK - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
Now FK's rotation numbers are 2,13,21,29, ...<br>
<br>
FK feels this is fair since it was accidental and NB is against it because they see it as no punishment at all.<br>
<br>
--------------<br>
Elaundar's counter-counter-proposal is to punish the number of rotation spots they skipped:<br>
SotE - FK - NB - TL - LoM - VoF - LoL - BotS <br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - VoF - LoL - BotS - FK<br>
SotE - NB - TL - LoM - VoF - LoL - BotS - FK<br>
With this, then FK rotation numbers are 2,16,24,32.  This is basically Sylph's comment, but is precise that they do not go before SotE on this round.<br>
<br>
In other words, FK illegally gained 3 positions so they should loose 3 positions. I really don't care what the punishment is that FK gets, but the it will establish the precidence.<br>
